      <title>AP(Affinity Propagation)学习</title>
      <link href="/2022/05/24/ap-affinity-propagation-xue-xi/"/>
      <url>/2022/05/24/ap-affinity-propagation-xue-xi/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>[TOC]</p><h3 id="一、AP算法介绍"><a href="#一、AP算法介绍" class="headerlink" title="一、AP算法介绍"></a>一、AP算法介绍</h3><p>AP（Affinity Propagation）算法由 Brendan Frey 和 Delbert Dueck 于 2007 年在《科学》杂志上首次发表。AP算法被翻译为近邻传播算法或者是亲和力传播算法，是一种聚类算法。但是与传统的聚类算法相比，AP算法不需要指定簇的数量。其核心思想是：所有样本点都是潜在的聚类中心点，数据点通过相似性矩阵两者相互连线，通过边的消息传递来计算样本的聚类中心。</p><ol><li>相似度矩阵（Similarity Matrix）</li></ol><p>根据给定的数据集A(m×n)，计算出相似矩阵S(m×m)。S(i，j)表示两样本数据点的负平方距离（即相似度）：<br>$$<br>s(i,j)=-||x_i-x_j||<br>$$</p><ol start="2"><li>吸引度矩阵（Responsibility Matrix）</li></ol><p>初始化矩阵元素为0，然后使用以下公式计算矩阵中的元素值（即该位置元素值等于其减去该行除该元素外的最大值）：</p><img src="C:\Users\PYZ\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220524193228334.png" alt="image-20220524193228334" style="zoom: 50%;"><p>其中i代表矩阵相关行，k代表列，初始化的归属度矩阵a为0</p><ol start="3"><li>归属度矩阵（Availability Matrix）</li></ol><p>初始化矩阵元素为0，使用单独的方程计算更新矩阵对角线的元素（即对角线元素值等于该列中除去对角线的元素后，其他正元素相加之和）：</p><img src="C:\Users\PYZ\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220524193448735.png" alt="image-20220524193448735" style="zoom:50%;"><p>同时，使用下面公式更新非对角元素的值（即该元素值等于0和该列对角元素值与除去该位置后正值的和，取较小值）：</p><img src="C:\Users\PYZ\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220524194050496.png" alt="image-20220524194050496" style="zoom:50%;"><p>其中i代表矩阵相关行，k代表列</p><h3 id="二、AP算法实现过程"><a href="#二、AP算法实现过程" class="headerlink" title="二、AP算法实现过程"></a>二、AP算法实现过程</h3><p>AP算法实现步骤：</p><ol><li>输入数据集D；</li><li>根据输入数据集D，计算相似度矩阵S；</li><li>初始化两个矩阵：吸引度矩阵R和归属度矩阵A；</li><li>根据上面的公式，交替迭代更新矩阵R和A；</li><li>直到满足收敛条件（边在迭代中保持不变或达到设定的迭代次数），阻尼系数。</li></ol><h3 id="三、AP算法编程实现"><a href="#三、AP算法编程实现" class="headerlink" title="三、AP算法编程实现"></a>三、AP算法编程实现</h3><pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token string">""</span>"<span class="token keyword">from</span> sklearn<span class="token punctuation">.</span>cluster <span class="token keyword">import</span> AffinityPropagation<span class="token keyword">from</span> sklearn <span class="token keyword">import</span> metrics<span class="token keyword">from</span> sklearn<span class="token punctuation">.</span>datasets <span class="token keyword">import</span> make_blobs<span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># %%</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Generate sample data</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># --------------------</span>centers <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>X<span class="token punctuation">,</span> labels_true <span class="token operator">=</span> make_blobs<span class="token punctuation">(</span>    n_samples<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">300</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> centers<span class="token operator">=</span>centers<span class="token punctuation">,</span> cluster_std<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">0.5</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> random_state<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># %%</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Compute Affinity Propagation</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># ----------------------------</span>af <span class="token operator">=</span> AffinityPropagation<span class="token punctuation">(</span>preference<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">50</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> random_state<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>fit<span class="token punctuation">(</span>X<span class="token punctuation">)</span>cluster_centers_indices <span class="token operator">=</span> af<span class="token punctuation">.</span>cluster_centers_indices_labels <span class="token operator">=</span> af<span class="token punctuation">.</span>labels_n_clusters_ <span class="token operator">=</span> len<span class="token punctuation">(</span>cluster_centers_indices<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Estimated number of clusters: %d"</span> <span class="token operator">%</span> n_clusters_<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Homogeneity: %0.3f"</span> <span class="token operator">%</span> metrics<span class="token punctuation">.</span>homogeneity_score<span class="token punctuation">(</span>labels_true<span class="token punctuation">,</span> labels<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Completeness: %0.3f"</span> <span class="token operator">%</span> metrics<span class="token punctuation">.</span>completeness_score<span class="token punctuation">(</span>labels_true<span class="token punctuation">,</span> labels<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"V-measure: %0.3f"</span> <span class="token operator">%</span> metrics<span class="token punctuation">.</span>v_measure_score<span class="token punctuation">(</span>labels_true<span class="token punctuation">,</span> labels<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Adjusted Rand Index: %0.3f"</span> <span class="token operator">%</span> metrics<span class="token punctuation">.</span>adjusted_rand_score<span class="token punctuation">(</span>labels_true<span class="token punctuation">,</span> labels<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>    <span class="token string">"Adjusted Mutual Information: %0.3f"</span>    <span class="token operator">%</span> metrics<span class="token punctuation">.</span>adjusted_mutual_info_score<span class="token punctuation">(</span>labels_true<span class="token punctuation">,</span> labels<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>    <span class="token string">"Silhouette Coefficient: %0.3f"</span>    <span class="token operator">%</span> metrics<span class="token punctuation">.</span>silhouette_score<span class="token punctuation">(</span>X<span class="token punctuation">,</span> labels<span class="token punctuation">,</span> metric<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"sqeuclidean"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># %%</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Plot result</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># -----------</span><span class="token keyword">import</span> matplotlib<span class="token punctuation">.</span>pyplot <span class="token keyword">as</span> plt<span class="token keyword">from</span> itertools <span class="token keyword">import</span> cycleplt<span class="token punctuation">.</span>close<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"all"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>plt<span class="token punctuation">.</span>figure<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>plt<span class="token punctuation">.</span>clf<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>colors <span class="token operator">=</span> cycle<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"bgrcmykbgrcmykbgrcmykbgrcmyk"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token keyword">for</span> k<span class="token punctuation">,</span> col <span class="token keyword">in</span> zip<span class="token punctuation">(</span>range<span class="token punctuation">(</span>n_clusters_<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> colors<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    class_members <span class="token operator">=</span> labels <span class="token operator">==</span> k    cluster_center <span class="token operator">=</span> X<span class="token punctuation">[</span>cluster_centers_indices<span class="token punctuation">[</span>k<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>    plt<span class="token punctuation">.</span>plot<span class="token punctuation">(</span>X<span class="token punctuation">[</span>class_members<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> X<span class="token punctuation">[</span>class_members<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> col <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">"."</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>    plt<span class="token punctuation">.</span>plot<span class="token punctuation">(</span>        cluster_center<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        cluster_center<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        <span class="token string">"o"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        markerfacecolor<span class="token operator">=</span>col<span class="token punctuation">,</span>        markeredgecolor<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"k"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>        markersize<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token number">14</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token punctuation">)</span>    <span class="token keyword">for</span> x <span class="token keyword">in</span> X<span class="token punctuation">[</span>class_members<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>        plt<span class="token punctuation">.</span>plot<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span>cluster_center<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> x<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span>cluster_center<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> x<span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> col<span class="token punctuation">)</span>plt<span class="token punctuation">.</span>title<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Estimated number of clusters: %d"</span> <span class="token operator">%</span> n_clusters_<span class="token punctuation">)</span>plt<span class="token punctuation">.</span>show<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></code></pre><p>结果实例：</p><pre><code>Estimated number of clusters: 3Homogeneity: 0.872Completeness: 0.872V-measure: 0.872Adjusted Rand Index: 0.912Adjusted Mutual Information: 0.871Silhouette Coefficient: 0.753</code></pre><p>画图：</p><p><img src="C:\Users\PYZ\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20220524211404861.png" alt="image-20220524211404861"></p><h3 id="四、总结"><a href="#四、总结" class="headerlink" title="四、总结"></a>四、总结</h3><p>AP算法优点：</p><ol><li>无需提前知道聚类个数；</li><li>对原始数据不敏感；</li><li>对距离矩阵的对称性无要求；</li><li>将数据作为聚类中心，而不是样本点的均值。</li></ol><p>AP算法缺点：</p><ol><li><p>算法的复杂度较高；</p></li><li><p>参考度（对角线元素作为聚类中心的可能性）和阻力系数影响较大。</p></li></ol><h3 id="五、参考"><a href="#五、参考" class="headerlink" title="五、参考"></a>五、参考</h3><p>Scikit-learn. (n.d.). <em>2.3. Clustering — scikit-learn 0.22.2 documentation</em>. scikit-learn: machine learning in Python — scikit-learn 0.16.1 documentation. Retrieved April 18, 2020, from <a href="https://scikit-learn.org/stable/modules/clustering.html#affinity-propagation">https://scikit-learn.org/stable/modules/clustering.html#affinity-propagation</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
